{"tid":380692,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Macbook pro 壞左flash drive，要4千維修費","createTime":"2017-08-30T10:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T13:19:46.000Z","uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"910c07d19018eb944e244fc65d22ac4eb8f554aa","tid":380692,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T10:29:38.000Z","msg":"幾個月前壞左，果時開左post問，但前幾日先拎去問價<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>有晚開著部機dowload野咁訓教<br />\n第二朝部機冇晒電，我即刻叉住電咁繼續用部機<br />\n用左陣，死左機，滑鼠變彩虹波，合埋蓋仍然著燈<br />\n<br />\n咁我reboot左好多次，一樣出現蘋果logo下 loading bar都係到7成就唔郁，隔多陣出現 禁止符號<br />\n然後我按住command+option+r+p咁開機，終於見到登入畫面，但登入完，loading bar都係到7成就唔郁，隔多陣出現 禁止符號<br />\n<br />\n重覆左好多次後，試下按著command+option+r咁開機 打算修復os，點知搵唔到hardisk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote>"},{"pid":"4ef17510468c7367125df6eb3062fa9a55e1db21","tid":380692,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T10:30:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"429294e900ca06f4363990c2f882e9300cf97b33","tid":380692,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"未打完覆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前幾日拎左去Apple authorized既 華x檢查，就話<br />\n<blockquote>After our inspection we found out flash drive fail and need to replace flash drive.&quot;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣整既話要4千，我保養期一早過左但又冇買apple care，有冇解決方法/ 平d既維修鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸：macbook pro 13&quot; early 2015(retina moon)"},{"pid":"ec6241115f43e7131fcc23d7ddbc3dbbcbf74fc2","tid":380692,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7caf2f407bc79754504d1e6ccebf11592cadabe","tid":380692,"uid":40903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0